snippet.title: Piers Morgan Calls Meghan Markle's 'Ellen' Intv 'Vomit-Making'
snippet.description:
Piers Morgan is once again putting Meghan Markle on blast. The British media personality wasn't a fan of the Duchess of Sussex's surprise appearance on "Ellen" this week, calling the collab a "vomit-making" "cheese-fest" that presented Meghan as a "desperate reality TV star" rather than a member of the royal family. Though Piers has been a longtime critic of Meghan and Harry's exit from royal duties, many fans were delighted to see the mom of two relaxed and up for some harmless fun.
